  "lines": [
    {
      "start": {"x": 1, "y": 1},
      "end": {"x": 5, "y": 20}
    },
    {
      "start": {"x": 3, "y": 15},
      "end": {"x": 10, "y": 2}
    }
  ]
}

Odcinki Współliniwe :
{
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": {"x": 5, "y": 5},
      "end": {"x": 10, "y": 10}
    },
    {
      "start": {"x": 5, "y": 5},
      "end": {"x": 10, "y": 10}
    }

{
  "lines": [
    {

      "end": {"x": 8, "y": 8}
    },
